/** @defgroup juce JUCE bindings
	The Limes JUCE API bindings.

	This group includes JUCE modules that wrap the Limes libraries,
	and some example plugins built using these modules.

	@dependency \b JUCE
	@parblock
	The JUCE library is required.

	You can set the environment or command-line variable \c JUCE_PATH to direct the Limes CMake configuration to use a local copy.
	If no local copy is present and JUCE cannot be found on your system, invoking Limes's CMake configuration will fetch and cache a copy of the JUCE source code.
	@endparblock

	@envvar \b JUCE_PATH
	This variable can be set to the root directory of a local copy of the JUCE repository.

	@cmakeopt \b LIMES_BUILD_EXAMPLE_PLUGINS If \c ON , some example
	plugins using Limes audio effects will be built. This option
	defaults to \c OFF .
 */

